oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.flex.runtime.event
Interface BCModelerListener

All Superinterfaces:
java.util.EventListener, ModelerListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
BCModelerAdapter, ServiceEnabler
public interface BCModelerListener
extends ModelerListener

An interface for objects to listen to the events occurred in a BCModeler. The implementation must always have a default constructor.

Listener classes should extend BCModelerAdapter instead of implementing this interface directly. If necessary, a class defined in package oracle.apps.fnd or any of its subpackages is allowed to implement this interface directly.
